# TraceRoot UI — Full Implementation Plan (From Scratch)

> **Goal**: Build the complete Next.js frontend for TraceRoot, fully compatible with the existing Python backend (Stages 1-9 of the KAN pipeline), including pattern matching display, feedback collection, intelligence metadata surfacing, and all telemetry flows.

---

## Architecture Summary

```
YOUR NEW UI (Next.js 14 App Router)
├── BFF Proxy Layer (api/ routes)         ← Proxies 9 endpoints to Python backend
├── Direct MongoDB Layer (api/ routes)    ← 6 endpoints skip Python backend
├── Pages                                  ← 4 authenticated pages + auth pages
├── Components                             ← ~25 core components
└── State Management                       ← React Context + URL params
         │
         ▼
Python FastAPI Backend (already built)
├── TelemetryRouter  → Jaeger/AWS/Tencent
├── ChatRouterClass  → KAN Pipeline → LLM → GitHub API
└── InternalRouter   → OTLP usage tracking
```

---

## Implementation Phases

| Phase | What You Build | Depends On | Estimated Effort |
|-------|----------------|------------|-----------------|
| **Phase 1** | Project setup + design system + layout shell | Nothing | 1-2 days |
| **Phase 2** | Auth (Clerk) + sidebar navigation | Phase 1 | 1 day |
| **Phase 3** | Settings page (provider config) | Phase 2 | 1-2 days |
| **Phase 4** | Integrate page (token management) | Phase 2 | 1 day |
| **Phase 5** | Trace list panel (left panel) | Phase 3 (needs provider config) | 2-3 days |
| **Phase 6** | Log view panel (right panel) | Phase 5 | 1-2 days |
| **Phase 7** | Trace waterfall view | Phase 5 | 1-2 days |
| **Phase 8** | Agent chat panel (core) | Phase 5 + Phase 6 | 3-4 days |
| **Phase 9** | Chat history + metadata + reasoning | Phase 8 | 1-2 days |
| **Phase 10** | GitHub action flow | Phase 8 | 1 day |
| **Phase 11** | Intelligence metadata + feedback UI | Phase 8 | 1-2 days |
| **Phase 12** | Source code context viewer | Phase 6 | 1 day |
| **Phase 13** | Polish + responsive + testing | All phases | 2-3 days |

**Total: ~17-25 days**

---

## PHASE 1: Project Setup + Design System

### 1.1 Initialize Next.js Project

```bash
npx -y create-next-app@latest ./ --typescript --tailwind --eslint --app --src-dir --import-alias "@/*"
```

### 1.2 Install Dependencies

```bash
# UI Components
npm install @radix-ui/react-hover-card @radix-ui/react-dialog @radix-ui/react-dropdown-menu
npm install @radix-ui/react-tabs @radix-ui/react-tooltip @radix-ui/react-collapsible
npm install @radix-ui/react-select @radix-ui/react-popover @radix-ui/react-checkbox
npm install class-variance-authority clsx tailwind-merge

# Icons
npm install lucide-react react-icons

# Auth
npm install @clerk/nextjs

# Database (for direct MongoDB routes)
npm install mongoose

# Utilities
npm install date-fns uuid
```

