## PHASE 8: Agent Chat Panel (Core)

### 8.1 API Routes

#### [NEW] [src/app/api/chat/route.ts](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/app/api/chat/route.ts)
- POST: Proxies to `REST_API_ENDPOINT/v1/explore/post-chat`
- Request body: [ChatRequest](file:///c:/traceroot-main/rest/config/chat.py#16-33) (message, trace_id, span_ids, model, mode, chat_id, providers)
- Response: [ChatResponse](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/models/chat.ts#56-61) with [ChatbotResponse](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/models/chat.ts#46-55) containing [metadata](file:///c:/traceroot-main/src/routing/response_builder.py#325-367) (IntelligenceMetadata)
- Fallback: Static response when `REST_API_ENDPOINT` not set

#### [NEW] [src/app/api/get_chat_history/route.ts](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/app/api/get_chat_history/route.ts)
- GET: Proxies to `/v1/explore/get-chat-history`

### 8.2 UI Components

#### [NEW] [src/components/right-panel/agent/Agent.tsx](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/components/right-panel/agent/Agent.tsx) (~700 lines)

**The chat orchestrator.** Key responsibilities:

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| Chat state | Messages array, loading state, current chat_id |
| Send message | `POST /api/chat` with full request body |
| Receive response | Parse [ChatResponse](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/models/chat.ts#56-61), extract [metadata](file:///c:/traceroot-main/src/routing/response_builder.py#325-367) |
| Polling | Every 1s poll `GET /api/get_chat_history` for GitHub/statistics messages |
| Multi-tab | Support multiple chat tabs per trace |
| Auto-scroll | Scroll to bottom on new message |
| Error handling | Show error message in chat if API fails |

```typescript
// Core message flow
const sendMessage = async (message: string) => {
  // 1. Add user message to UI (optimistic)
  setMessages(prev => [...prev, userMessage]);
  
  // 2. Send to backend
  const response = await fetch("/api/chat", {
    method: "POST",
    body: JSON.stringify({
      message, trace_id, span_ids, model, mode, chat_id,
      trace_provider, log_provider, provider
    })
  });
  
  // 3. Parse response with metadata
  const data: ChatResponse = await response.json();
  
  // 4. Add assistant message (includes metadata for Phase 11)
  setMessages(prev => [...prev, data.data]);
};
```

#### [NEW] [src/components/right-panel/agent/MessageInput.tsx](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/components/right-panel/agent/MessageInput.tsx)
