### 10.2 UI — Confirmation Buttons

In [ChatMessage.tsx](file:///c:/traceroot-main/ui/src/components/right-panel/agent/ChatMessage.tsx), when `status === "awaiting_confirmation"`:
```tsx
<div className="flex gap-2 mt-2">
  <Button variant="default" onClick={() => onSendMessage("yes")}>
    Yes, create it
  </Button>
  <Button variant="outline" className="text-red-500" onClick={() => onSendMessage("no")}>
    No, cancel
  </Button>
</div>
```

After confirmation, the response message renders GitHub URLs as clickable `PR #42` links.

