## PHASE 13: Polish + Testing

### 13.1 Responsive Design
- Mobile: sidebar collapses to hamburger menu
- Tablet: right panel stacks below left panel
- Desktop: full 3-panel layout

### 13.2 Loading States
- Trace list: skeleton rows while loading
- Chat: pulsing robot avatar with spinner
- Log view: skeleton lines

### 13.3 Error States
- Network error → toast notification
- Empty trace list → "No traces found" with time range suggestion
- Chat error → error message in chat bubble

### 13.4 Keyboard Shortcuts
- `Enter` → send message
- `Shift+Enter` → newline
- `Escape` → close dialogs

### 13.5 Testing Approach
- Verify each API route returns correct response shape
- Test chat flow end-to-end: message → response → references
- Test feedback flow: 👍/👎 → backend receives → stored in DB
- Test provider config: save/load/delete cycle
- Test with real Jaeger traces

